<ul>=20
<li style=3D"text-align: left;"><strong>On April 17, online scheduling will=
 no longer be available through MyVirginiaMason.</strong> If you need to sc=
hedule or change an appointment between April 17 and May 2, please call you=
r clinic or facility.</li>=20
</ul>=20
<ul>=20
<li style=3D"text-align: left;"><strong>On April 29, MyVirginiaMason will b=
ecome read-only.</strong> This means patient/provider messaging will not be=
 available through MyVirginiaMason.&nbsp;However, you will still be able to=
 view your historical health information. If you need to contact your provi=
der during this time, please call your clinic.</li>=20
</ul>=20
<ul>=20
<li style=3D"text-align: left;"><strong>On May 2, you will begin using the =
